query:
SELECT 
  fb.bidderName,
  fb.team,
  fb.bidAmount,
  fb.dropPlayer,
  fb.createdAt,
  p.name as playerName,
  p.overall
FROM fa_bids fb
JOIN players p ON fb.playerId = p.id
WHERE p.name LIKE '%Gradey Dick%'
ORDER BY fb.bidAmount DESC, fb.createdAt ASC;
